These are the instructions to perform an Account Recovery using Anchor on Android.  This assumes you are starting from the main home screen.
You will need a valid Owner Key Certificate (OKC) to complete this process.

1. Select "Add Account"
2. Select "Recover Account"
3. Scan QR Code from OKC (screen advances automatically)
4. Enter the 6 words from your OKC (screen advances automatically)
5. Select "Add New Key for this Device"
6. Select "Recover Account"
7. Select "Done"